column5: Anyone have any information on either of these outfitters? Both seem to be in the same general area. Thanks.

Stayed one time on Maseres Lake with Sennterra Outfitters in 2007. Fishing was ok. The problem is the cabins are on a hill over looking the lake. Steep and long road leading down to the docks. Pain hauling your gear up and down the hill. They are the only outfitters on the lake but there are some private cabins.
